---
import Link from "../../components/Link.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy">
  <h2>Privacy</h2>

  <p>
    This website is operated by Alexander Daichendt. You can contact me at <Link
      href="mailto:me@daichendt.one">me@daichendt.one</Link
    >.
  </p>

  <h2>Website Access</h2>
  <p>
    This website is hosted by Cloudflare. When you access the site, technical
    request data such as your IP address, browser information, requested URL,
    referrer, time of access, and response status may be processed to deliver
    the website and keep it secure.
  </p>

  <p>
    The legal basis is legitimate interest under Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR. Cloudflare
    may process data outside the EEA using appropriate safeguards. More
    information is available from <Link
      href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/"
      >Cloudflare's privacy policy</Link
    >.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    If you contact me by email, I process your email address and message content
    to reply to you. I delete correspondence when it is no longer needed, unless
    I have to keep it for legal or security reasons.
  </p>

  <h2>Analytics and Cookies</h2>
  <p>I do not use analytics or tracking cookies on this website.</p>

  <h2>Your Rights</h2>
  <p>
    Under the GDPR, you may request access, rectification, erasure, restriction,
    portability, or object to processing. You may also complain to the Norwegian
    Data Protection Authority, <Link href="https://www.datatilsynet.no/"
      >Datatilsynet</Link
    >.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
